  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Take off on a magical quest with Annika and her sister, Brieta - a flying horse! The evil Wenlock has turned everyone in the kingdom to stone and it's up to Annika and Brieta to reverse the spell! Play exciting mini-games and solve puzzles to defeat the wizard to restore the kingdom!",
